Celestia plugin

Celestia is a 3D space simulator program created by Chris Laurel, based on the Hipparcos Catalogue (HIP). For more information, see the README.txt file under the Apps/Celestia/bin directory.

Useful shortcuts :

[i] : show/hide clouds

Move observer :
[8] : Pitch down
[2] : Pitch up
[7] : Roll right 
[9] : Roll left